rows.label: qst620502_msg0004
rows.name:
There's been an uprising and 
everything's gone crazy.

rows.label: qst620502_msg0005
rows.name:
It's too much for us to handle
by ourselves, Highness. Might
we count on your aid?

rows.label: qst620502_msg0007
rows.name:
Maybe this is what Ibuki
was talking about back at the inn...

rows.label: qst620502_msg0008
rows.name:
Wait, maybe I remember
what it was...

rows.label: qst620502_msg0010
rows.name:
This is NOT the time for 
stupidity, ugh!

rows.label: qst620502_msg0011
rows.name:
It's not so bad, Ibuki. You heard that
a rebellion would take place within
the palace.

rows.label: qst620502_msg0012
rows.name:
The fact that you told us
about it right away meant
we were ready to move out.

rows.label: qst620502_msg0013
rows.name:
And here we are, right after
the whole thing happened,
ready to sort things out.

rows.label: qst620502_msg0015
rows.name:
Just when I thought she got it
together...

rows.label: qst620502_msg0016
rows.name:
Your Highness. The rebel soldiers are
heading for the forbidden gate that lies
beyond Puresnow Passage.

rows.label: qst620502_msg0017
rows.name:
Right, then. Sounds like a job
for the Zekenator. Let's go.

rows.label: qst620502_msg0018
rows.name:
Indeed. We need the situation
under control before we try
to find out what's gone on.
